Just put this into any object your character wears, configure the name, check instructions with /1 help
Should be similar enough to NF's chatter it's just pick up and go.
You DO NOT have to do /me in the chat to emote with this script, it handles all of that.

This is meant as a replacement so operates on channel 4 with similar commands. 
Remember to change your NF HUD's rp channel away from channel 4 by using: @rpchannel -99
or whichever random channel.
